WEBVTT

00:00:29.941 --> 00:00:32.539
izrađeno iz jednog komada.

00:00:32.845 --> 00:00:34.438
Nema sata,

00:00:34.462 --> 00:00:36.002
nema užeta,

00:00:36.026 --> 00:00:37.456
nema plahte.

00:00:38.022 --> 00:00:42.235
Jedan je komad izbijeljenog 
honduraškog mahagonija.

00:00:42.969 --> 00:00:44.659
Da pojasnim:

00:00:44.683 --> 00:00:49.411
poanta ove vježbe 
nije u promatranju skulpture.

00:00:50.509 --> 00:00:51.949
Poanta je u promatranju

00:00:52.440 --> 00:00:57.215
i spoznaji da pozorno promatranje 
može spasiti život,

00:00:57.239 --> 00:00:58.709
promijeniti vašu tvrtku,

00:00:58.733 --> 00:01:02.996
čak i pomoći da razumijete 
određena ponašanja vaše djece.